    <briefdescription>
<para>Editor Debugger Program - Control panel for simulation debugging. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Provides controls for:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Simulation control (Play, Stop, Step, Exit to Editor)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Settings access</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Snapshot management for world state capture and analysis</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para>Snapshot data is stored in context.sharedData[&quot;snapshots&quot;] as a list of snapshot names. Commands are issued to take snapshots, analyze them, or delete them. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
